{"tid":2227191,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"哆啦A夢2020電影討論區","createTime":"2020-10-02T14:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T06:12:39.000Z","uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6b414f00614b46ee4e3aa7451852076aaf106f0f","tid":2227191,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:51:09.000Z","msg":"本次電影的另一個主旨則是「演化」（進化）。對此木村認為，成長的意義，重點在於理解自己的極限。所謂的極限，指的是自己盡全力所能達到的程度。無論在什麼情況下都應該盡自己的全力，對於每一件事皆發揮 100% 的力量，才能理解自己的極限所在，「而當你能夠超越極限時，這對你來說就是『進化』。」木村希望大家看完這部電影之後都能好好思考這點。<br />\n<br />\n呢段真係講得好好"},{"pid":"9b9f1e3b14f707002c3e67bbb772cfaedfbc48ef","tid":2227191,"uid":17388,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:52:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"750febd5a63835ab9dbcf50421421787cb5acccf","tid":2227191,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:55:59.000Z","msg":"到而家仲未接受到冇保全叔聲音既多啦a夢<br />\n<br />\n希望遲d audio deepfake技術再成熟<br />\n會有人整<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877afe67e574f2416e010057b1dcc8d3c8d5cb80","tid":2227191,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:58:27.000Z","msg":"尖撚表示：Over training不了"},{"pid":"7499c0d6271e8aa42bfc8e5eb64552936d2dce85","tid":2227191,"uid":270967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T16:04:48.000Z","msg":"睇左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725f019cef49f100f8437ac804ec8509d52aaee0","tid":2227191,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T16:06:01.000Z","msg":"暫時未打完感想<br />\n打完再post"},{"pid":"fd7966acff788a8e836600cbccc81e5057d75fc6","tid":2227191,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T06:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}